{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>死者73歲姓劉，據了解是泳客。警員在泳灘的一個儲物櫃找到疑是死者的背包，已聯絡其家人跟進事件。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126454737558835200097521.jpeg/6vSGvjFvdTybzYVU4Y71MZ7t0a4-fJPy0M7Z7dDO2e0\" alt=\"大埔龍尾泳灘有泳客疑遇溺身亡。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>大埔龍尾泳灘有泳客疑遇溺身亡。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><p>據悉，劉翁是退休人士，家住元朗區，有晨泳習慣。今早7時左右，有泳客發現事主遇溺，於是報案。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126455266808696832803467.jpeg/sCbP3TXBCTSarBJfBZIVFAPn9WyzsXNtlKu56pSrueo\" alt=\"大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126455270319460352054689.jpeg/MwVx8OH9ncDz9wpjphu5E0N5yyXFzZJY9Tl6avU5emo\" alt=\"大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126455273675034624278463.jpeg/_mV8WF_18yV55Mp1RTyeiijTHFIJM13RJriZwCa4mcA\" alt=\"大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>大埔龍尾泳灘發生遇溺事故。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126445282238664704450291.jpeg/X0Klr6TrIBVTUqT9QSjEHWOoIC3BFAAraTmVOGk5lTg\" alt=\"七旬翁在沙灘疑遇溺，送院不治。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>七旬翁在沙灘疑遇溺，送院不治。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260430/1126453901428527104512839.jpeg/VIjgKBLtJ7ozZ9b3SPYsv_1r6uWzU_xnIiOMLyIjjC8\" alt=\"警員到場調查。（讀者提供）\"><figcaption>警員到場調查。（讀者提供）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T04:26:33.713712+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":211,"images":6,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}